thread.title: K Fowler

author: K Fowler
title: K Fowler
text: The process was simple and easy to understand. The rates were generous, the prepaid FedEx label made a big difference as the amount Quote: d is the amount you get. Fast payment into your PayPal account. Personal correspondence to let you know they had received the goods and when they had been processed. Couldn't have been happier. Will definitely use them again. Beats listing it on an auction site.
